{"tid":1009931,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[豬年只有地產不利!!]馬鞍山薈朗雙屍案 男上吊女伏屍單位內","createTime":"2019-02-05T14:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T03:02:45.000Z","uid":65346,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d70e16981c07c624c79bc0f07a670d922c4941d2","tid":1009931,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山發生雙屍案！晚上8時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指弟弟於馬錦街9號薈朗一單位內吊頸，警員到場發現<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男子</span>已經<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不治</span>，經調查後發現單位內有一具<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女屍</span>。警方正封鎖現場調查，氣氛緊張。"},{"pid":"ad4f7c53acfdb5a1b2fb20988fe3c3a9c5dfbff1","tid":1009931,"uid":43924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1070bccfdecaf5e322190e8d18068108023206fc","tid":1009931,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:18:28.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n下世咪再喺香港出生啦"},{"pid":"bbdb9c0a0dd537856803cb8f73cd33ea50b2958e","tid":1009931,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"有新樓住又有女咁都要死？"},{"pid":"4811dc7f2cc84c03e68263a9ea8b5d1a6212c8fc","tid":1009931,"uid":190540,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67b82e11c71fc8bc6a2a4c0187918df5f5c3e471","tid":1009931,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4811dc7f2cc84c03e68263a9ea8b5d1a6212c8fc","tid":1009931,"uid":190540,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:43:42.000Z","msg":"<im